  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      portable monitoring device could diagnose sleep apnea in high risk patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study of another larger cohort investigating different algorithms in managing
      patients suspected of sleep apnea using portable monitoring device.

      Portable monitoring device is applied simultaneously with PSG to compare it's accuracy and
      validity.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
